{
  "stem": "471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a marketplace like that there, where they have a well-known farmer's-- a well-known farmer's market back there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They pick me up from over there, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bingo, didn't see home for three weeks, maybe more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Three or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother had to go with my sister to Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- she-- over there, she had family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because she comes from Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have an uncle, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a brother, she had there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They brought me out from money, from Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the way I-- I got from over there, out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in a--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in that camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barracks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were digging those barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were digging, you know, the-- the room for the foundation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out for money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, she-- my uncle bribed the-- bribed the SS who was transporting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I tell you why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this was only about 20 kilometers from Tarnow, Pustkow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were some people, what they were living in Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were going every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- they would transport them back and forth to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at night, they were going home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So one night, he organize [? that ?] with the-- with the-- I don't know what kind of rank he had-- the SS man, that he call me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he grab me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He brought me to my uncle's house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then I find out that my mother bribed him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My uncle bribe him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He threw in a nice few hundreds dollars for that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At that point it was a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Back to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe a month.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was my first experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here, what I start to smell what the Germans are.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
